what_worked: Applied dimension_cte_isolate: Applied dimension_cte_isolate strategy by extracting small filtered dimension tables (address, income_band) into CTEs first, then progressively building join paths through household demographics and customer demographics before the final join with the large fact table (store_returns). This creates small hash tables for early filtering and reduces the working set before the expensive fact table join.
why_it_worked: Pre-filtering all dimension tables into CTEs avoids repeated full-table scans
